data.description: Stunning 5 bedroom 3.5 bath home, walkout basement, newly fenced large back yard. Entertain in the Chef's kitchen with 8 burner gas range, double oven, custom range hood, pot filler, under counter microwave, waterfall edged quartz countertops, gorgeous backsplash, custom cabinetry with lighting, beverage counter & beautiful pantry. 2 sided fireplace in main floor living room and screened porch plus one in the basement family room. Main floor features 3 bedroom 2 1/2 baths. Basement features 2 bedrooms, 1 full bath, theatre (prewired for surround sound), bonus & panic rooms. New screened porch just outside basement. 2 car attached garage plus a utility garage in the rear. Stamped concrete fire pit. Ecobee thermostat. Near walk trail & park. With an acceptable offer the seller will contribute up to 3% towards buyers' closing costs, prepaids and/or buy down (the first year interest rate is 2% below the current market).
